name: Short sleeved cotton baby bodysuit or onesie
description:
This is a single plain short sleeved bodysuit or onesie in pure rib cotton. Made from a beautiful quality fabric that will hold it's shape well after washing and tumble drying. It has an envelope neckline and sweet picot detail on the neckband and sleeves. Use it as a perfect blank canvas for your creativity. Embellish it with fabric, embroidery or buttons to create a unique garment, or leave it plain. See the other listings if you want more than one bodysuit - bulk discounts apply.
Available in size newborn (000), 3-6 months (00) and 6-12 months (0).
